title: Michigan State University Education in Asia Series
additional-notes: This is a monographic series.  Before concluding a volume is in the public domain, search for renewals for a volume under its distinctive title. We have not systematically checked volume titles for this serial.

We have only found one volume of this serial in WorldCat, and at Michigan State University's library.  The volume, 'Education and Development in India and Pakistan: A Select and Annotated Bibliography' by Cole Speicher Brembeck and Edward W. Weidner, appears not to have a copyright renewal or a copyright notice.
acknowledgement: Thanks to Shelton Henderson for copyright research on this title.
